_:Ne360a46941304e4694826b624a8486f9 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Kate Bell is Assistant General Secretary at the <abbr title=\"Trades Union Congress\">TUC</abbr>, responsible for inter-union relations and leads on <abbr title=\"Trades Union Congress\">TUC</abbr> internal matters. Kate joined the <abbr title=\"Trades Union Congress\">TUC</abbr> in 2016 as the organisation’s head of economics, international and employment rights. She played a leading role in representing the views of working people during the pandemic. Before working in the <abbr title=\"Trades Union Congress\">TUC</abbr>, Kate worked as Head of Policy and Public Affairs for a local authority and has also worked for the charities Child Poverty Action Group and Gingerbread.</p>\n\n" .
